#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.159"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.159:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:0.2"
msgid "15. Diṭṭhivagga "
msgstr "15. Views "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.159:0.3"
msgid "159. Ānandasutta "
msgstr "159. With Ānanda "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.159:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā … pe … bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:1.3"
msgid "“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto vihareyyan”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.188, sc2
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ānanda, "
msgstr "“What do you think, Ānanda? "

msgctxt "sn22.159:2.2"
msgid "rūpaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "Is form permanent or impermanent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.3"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.4"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.5"
msgid "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Suffering, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.6"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, kallaṃ nu taṃ samanupassituṃ: "
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, suffering, and liable to fall apart, is it fit to be regarded thus: "

msgctxt "sn22.159:2.7"
msgid "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’”ti? "
msgstr "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.8"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.9"
msgid "“Vedanā … "
msgstr "“Is feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.159:2.10"
msgid "saññā … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.159:2.11"
msgid "saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.159:2.12"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "consciousness permanent or impermanent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.13"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.14"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.15"
msgid "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Suffering, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.16"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, kallaṃ nu taṃ samanupassituṃ: "
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, suffering, and liable to fall apart, is it fit to be regarded thus: "

msgctxt "sn22.159:2.17"
msgid "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’”ti? "
msgstr "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: hetaṃ, bhante → no hetaṃ bhante. tasmātihānanda yaṃ kiñci rūpaṃ atītānāgatapaccuppannaṃ …pe… daṭṭhabbaṃ. (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.18"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.19"
msgid "“Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "“Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn22.159:2.20"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.21"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.159:2.22"
msgid "Diṭṭhivaggo pañcamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn22.159:3.1"
msgid "Ajjhattikaṃ etaṃmama, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.159:3.2"
msgid "Soattā nocamesiyā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.159:3.3"
msgid "Micchāsakkāyattānu dve, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.159:3.4"
msgid "Abhinivesā ānandenāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.159:3.5"
msgid "Uparipaṇṇāsako samatto. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="vagguddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn22.159:4.1"
msgid "Anto dhammakathikā vijjā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.159:4.2"
msgid "kukkuḷaṃ diṭṭhipañcamaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.159:4.3"
msgid "Tatiyo paṇṇāsako vutto, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: nipātoti pavuccatīti → nipāto tena vuccatīti (bj) | nipāto tena pavuccati (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn22.159:4.4"
msgid "nipātoti pavuccatīti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn22.159:4.5"
msgid "Khandhasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on the aggregates are complete."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
